  "text": [
    "came in a pink,",
    "orange and white",
    "striped metal tube,",
    "with a black curlicue",
    "border and a splayed",
    "gold base. It came",
    "in any number of",
    "mod shades: Nippy",
    "Beige, Chelsea Pink,",
    "Poppycock, Hot Nec-",
    "taringo, Pinkadilly,",
    "Dicey Peach. There",
    "were several tubes in",
    "my mother\u2019s makeup",
    "drawer in the bath-",
    "room five out of six",
    "of us used (my father",
    "had his own bathroom,",
    "as forbidden as the",
    "walk-in closet where",
    "his",
    "were",
    "hidden under a stack",
    "of sweaters on the top",
    "shelf). All the girls",
    "at school had Slicker",
    "in their purses; I",
    "watched them apply",
    "The London Look",
    "at the beginning and",
    "end of each class. I",
    "marveled at what else",
    "spilled out: compact,",
    "mascara brush, eye",
    "shadow, wallet, troll",
    "doll, dyed rabbit\u2019s",
    "foot, chewing gum,",
    "tampon, pink plastic",
    "comb. At home I",
    "stared at myself in",
    "the medicine cabinet",
    "mirror and, as my",
    "brother pounded",
    "on the locked bath-",
    "room door, twisted",
    "a tube and rubbed,",
    "ever so slightly,",
    "Slicker on my lips."
  ],
